## Agent Lifecycle Management

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Registration
    Registration --> HealthCheck
    HealthCheck --> Ready
    Ready --> Execution: run() called
    Execution --> Success: completed
    Execution --> TransientError: network/timeout
    TransientError --> Retry: exponential backoff
    Retry --> Execution
    TransientError --> CircuitOpen: max retries
    CircuitOpen --> HalfOpen: timeout
    HalfOpen --> Closed: success
    HalfOpen --> Open: failure
    Execution --> Fallback: permanent failure
    Fallback --> Ready
    Ready --> HealthCheck: periodic
```

**Retry Logic**:
- Max retries: 3 (configurable per agent)
- Backoff: 60s, 120s, 240s (exponential)
- Circuit Breaker: 5 failures → 60s open → half-open test

**Graceful Degradation**:
- Primary agent fails → fallback agent (if configured)
- All failures logged with correlation IDs
- Partial results preserved in context

